---
import BaseLayout from "~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Tattoo portfolio"
  description="A minimal, single-page photo gallery for Astro.">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center pt-20">
        <h1 class="text-2xl pb-4 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        <div class="flex flex-col items-start max-w-md w-full">
            <div>
                <p class="font-bold">How long for a tattoo to heal?</p>
                <p class="pb-4">Anywhere from two to three weeks</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p class="font-bold">Is itching normal?</p>
                <p class="pb-4">Itching is a normal healing process</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p class="font-bold">Clear film is full with blood, is that normal?</p>
                <p class="pb-4">Yes, some people have more blood than others</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p class="font-bold">How long do i leave the clear film on?</p>
                <p class="pb-4">Leave the clear film on for two weeks then take it off in the shower</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p class="font-bold">Is it supposed to hurt?</p>
                <p class="pb-4">The pain should go away in a couple days, if not then visit us to have a look</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p class="font-bold">Do I have to moisturize daily?</p>
                <p class="pb-4">You should moisturize every four hours with a light amount of regular skin lotion</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <p class="font-bold">What if we can't finish in one session?</p>
                <p class="pb-4">We can finish your tattoo the next day if you need a break, no worries</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>